  "faq": {
    "what_is_flowb": "What is FlowB?",
    "what_is_flowb_answer": "FlowB is your event companion app. We aggregate side events, hackathons, parties, and meetups into one place so you never miss what matters. Form crews with friends, earn points, and explore together.",
    "how_earn_points": "How do I earn points?",
    "how_earn_points_answer": "RSVP to events, check in at venues with your crew, invite friends, complete daily quests, and engage with the community. Points unlock milestones and leaderboard rankings.",
    "what_are_crews": "What are crews?",
    "what_are_crews_answer": "Crews are groups of friends exploring events together. Create or join a crew to coordinate schedules, check in together at events, and earn bonus crew points.",
